{"tid":177340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人類最恐怖】住「棺材屋」轉個身都難   真實生活其實係咁","createTime":"2017-03-28T19:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T08:02:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a171513a962eefbea669c5fd0f1b8c30c2b13cd","tid":177340,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:13:39.000Z","msg":"2017年03月29日<br />\n【人類最恐怖】住「棺材屋」轉個身都難 乳牛真實生活其實係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490692163_0095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490692163_0095.jpg&h=2fb72a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490692162_352e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490692162_352e.jpg&h=5a9933a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國多塞特郡多徹斯特附近一個乳牛養殖場，被揭發虐待乳牛，一隻隻乳牛只能居住在狹窄的「棺材屋」，慘變成擠迫戶，環境極不人道。<br />\n<br />\n從拍攝的照片看到，養殖場內的乳牛住在一個個細小、獨立的「棺材屋」，由於地方太狹小，牛隻想爬回屋內，都要費盡氣力才能成功，部份牛隻也因為居住環境擠迫，導致身體多處擦傷。根據英國法例規定，只有8周及以下的牛隻才能居住在獨立的飼養屋內，但現場所見有些牛隻已經六個月大，明顯違規。<br />\n該養殖場的乳牛長大後，便會被運到英國不同的農場產奶，牠們的奶製品會供應予馬莎等大型超市集團。馬莎發言人表示，對照片感到「失望及完全不能接受」，願意與有關方面合作，立即採取行動糾正問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170329/56490684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170329%2F56490684&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=8d43b000\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170329%2F56490684&h=7b2fe63d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170329/56490684</a>"},{"pid":"e20ad86e9a03c3a9f1345143eadfc31a380ac231","tid":177340,"uid":94663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:43:22.000Z","msg":"d 牛 心諗 喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1d5094e630e5df43d6723731c678282c5a50aa","tid":177340,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f856a6c16ba603f5a70c9a20f281a1461090907c","tid":177340,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"籠屋 (牛牛Version)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62ef33d9d06fee0ce36db1ec3ef40bb3a2d2dcd","tid":177340,"uid":9782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T21:47:11.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為講深水埗籠屋"},{"pid":"ca4147d7f86374876cc33a95fbffb16a2a796753","tid":177340,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T22:04:51.000Z","msg":"有山景仲想點"},{"pid":"b3a04cb604c4dca984398f9071e91699e15c09b7","tid":177340,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇標題以為講深水埗籠屋</blockquote><br />\n香港人仲低賤過啲牛"},{"pid":"5594147a7c947e73c6a7ccc61eda6604b2e0f0fd","tid":177340,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇標題以為講深水埗籠屋</blockquote><br />\n香港人仲低賤過啲牛</blockquote><br />\n外國牛仲多人關注過香港人"},{"pid":"72af140deb7d7a0639824be60f03847f67df287a","tid":177340,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:11:11.000Z","msg":"英國仲有土地；本港則架床疊「屋」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1669e464a3474b84f80725d5e3f7d998174df0fa","tid":177340,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:17:50.000Z","msg":"以為係新樓盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ac9df55dac951e36c230080b2e687e8f5aae